fn.p:
Male-related experiments removed to focus on female CRZ/CrzR signaling in post-mating response (PMR);
Added RT-PCR/immunohistochemistry data confirming no CRZ in Drosophila melanogaster male accessory glands;
Refined stats (chi-square for proportions, GLM for time-series) and added heterozygote assays (recessive Crz, dominant CrzR phenotypes);
Corrected text/figures: standardized "D. melanogaster", oviposition Y-axis labels ("Number of eggs per female within 3 days"), color schemes, and added sample sizes per replicate to legends;
Restructured abstract thematically; expanded Discussion to highlight CRZ-GnRH conservation and future directions; removed redundant intro content.
